{"name": "stl2cad", "metadata": {"name": "stl2cad", "version": "0.2.0", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["click"], "summary": "Convert STL to CAD formats.", "upload_time": 1733876207}, "documentation": ["# STL2CAD\n\nA lightweight utility to convert STL files into CAD formats.\n\n```\nstl2cad geometry.stl -o geometry.step\n```\n\n## Dependencies\nThe `stl2cad` package depends on [FreeCAD](https://www.freecad.org/), which can be downloaded \n[here](https://www.freecad.org/downloads.php).\nThe FreeCAD Python modules must also be on the Python path for `stl2cad` to work.\n\nAn example script of downloading and setting up FreeCAD in a Linux environment is provided below.\n\n```\nmkdir freecad\ncd freecad\n\nwget https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/releases/download/1.0.0/FreeCAD_1.0.0-conda-Linux-x86_64-py311.AppImage\n\nchmod -v +x ~/Downloads/FreeCAD_*.AppImage\n./FreeCAD_*.AppImage --appimage-extract\n```\n\n\n## To Do\n- clarify and test example install script (need to add to path)\n- add better examples\n- add tests\n- allow saving multiple formats in one go (more efficient)\n"], "modules": [{"name": "stl2cad", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "stl2cad.cli", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "stl2cad.cli.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "infile", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "outfile", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "cadfile", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "verbose", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "stl2cad.utilities", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "stl2cad.utilities.create_new_document", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "doc_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Create a new FreeCAD document."]}, {"name": "stl2cad.utilities.import_stl", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "file_path", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "object_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "verbose", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Import an STL file and return a mesh object."]}, {"name": "stl2cad.utilities.shape_from_mesh", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "mesh_object", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "tolerance", "type": {"name": "float", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.float", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "sewing", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "verbose", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Convert a mesh object to a shape."]}, {"name": "stl2cad.utilities.make_solid", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "shape_object", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "verbose", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Create a solid from a shape object."]}, {"name": "stl2cad.ut